latestPosts.caption:
Powered Couple (Part 1)
This photoshoot is an ode to the time we’ve spent away from one another. In this period of communicating and sharing our lives living worlds away, we became one - to the extent that his individual experience in New York became a memory as strong for me in India. 

Each other’s company became omnipresent, and the distance only tugged our string tighter. This series serves as a glimpse into our connection, strengthened by distance. Stay tuned for part 2 as we continue to tell our story.

This special project wouldn’t be made possible without a team that brought their A Game to the table 🧡

Photographer @thetiltedlens 
Stylist @ria.mediratta
HMUA @vaishnevidiwanne @getglossywith_nandinigoyal
Creative Directors & Models @akshatjha_ @_jessicasingh_
